{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc2827eaf-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s503"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"503"},"text":"§ 503.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Administrative error; equitable relief","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc2827eb0-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s503/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If the Secretary determines that benefits administered by the Department have not been provided by reason of administrative error on the part of the Federal Government or any of its employees, the Secretary may provide such relief on account of such error as the Secretary determines equitable, including the payment of moneys to any person whom the Secretary determines is equitably entitled to such moneys.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc2827eb1-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s503/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If the Secretary determines that a veteran, surviving spouse, child of a veteran, or other person has suffered loss as a consequence of reliance upon a determination by the Department of eligibility or entitlement to benefits, without knowledge that it was erroneously made, the Secretary may provide such relief on account of such error as the Secretary determines is equitable, including the payment of moneys to any person whom the Secretary determines is equitably entitled to such moneys.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc2827eb2-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s503/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Not later than April 1 of each year, the Secretary shall submit to Congress a report containing a statement as to the disposition of each case recommended to the Secretary for equitable relief under this section during the preceding calendar year. No report shall be required under this subsection after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2026-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2026","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc2827eb3-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/83/s2/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–83, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-08-06"},"text":"Aug. 6, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/386"},"text":"105 Stat. 386","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/419/tIV/s403/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–419, title IV, § 403(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-11-01"},"text":"Nov. 1, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1864"},"text":"114 Stat. 1864","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/233/tIV/s403"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–233, title IV, § 403","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-06-15"},"text":"June 15, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/411"},"text":"120 Stat. 411","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/275/tVIII/s808"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–275, title VIII, § 808","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-10-13"},"text":"Oct. 13, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/2893"},"text":"124 Stat. 2893","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/175/tIV/s403"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–175, title IV, § 403","child